                        style={{
                            fontSize: "1.5rem",
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            color: "#fff",
                            marginBottom: "1rem",
                        }}
                    >
                        2. Use of Coupons
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        CourseSpeak provides coupons and deal links for
                        third-party platforms like Udemy. We do not guarantee
                        the validity specific coupons as they may expire or be
                        changed by the provider at any time.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We are not responsible for any purchases made on
                        third-party sites.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section style={{ marginBottom: "2rem" }}>
                    <h2
                        style={{
                            fontSize: "1.5rem",
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            color: "#fff",
                            marginBottom: "1rem",
                        }}
                    >
                        3. User Conduct
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        You agree not to misuse our services, including
                        attempting to scrape data, interfere with site security,
                        or use the site for illegal purposes.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section style={{ marginBottom: "2rem" }}>
                    <h2
                        style={{
                            fontSize: "1.5rem",
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            color: "#fff",
                            marginBottom: "1rem",
                        }}
                    >
                        4. Intellectual Property
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        All content on CourseSpeak is property of CourseSpeak or
                        its licensors. Third-party trademarks (e.g., Udemy)
                        belong to their respective owners.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section
                    style={{
                        marginBottom: "2rem",
                        padding: "1.5rem",
                        background: "#1f2330",
                        borderRadius: "8px",
                    }}
                >
                    <h3
                        style={{
                            fontSize: "1.2rem",
                            fontWeight: 700,
                            color: "#fff",
                            marginBottom: "0.5rem",
                        }}
                    >
                        Contact Legal
                    </h3>
                    <p>
                        For extensive inquiries regarding these terms, please
                        contact us at <a
                            href="mailto:legal@coursespeak.com"
                            style={{ color: "#3b82f6" }}
                            >legal@coursespeak.com</a
                        >.
